lpchaim 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10611] added a 
``url decode``
 command
dmatos2012 fixed an issue in 
``ucp``
: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10609] "Change error when directory is specified but not recursive"
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10604] removed underline from std NU_LOG_FORMAT
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10583] added a few more grid icons
gaetschwartz updated 
``std log``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10603] allow specifying a custom date format
lavafroth fixed a bug with 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10600] path completions surrounded by quotes or backticks
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10543] Fish-like completions for nested directories
jntrnr made improvements to 
``cd``
: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10588] removed cd w/ abbreviations
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10585] allowed auto-cd on trailing slash
hudclark added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10489] new 
``unfold``
 command
sholderbach made some parsing+type improvements: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10581] Parse custom completer annotation only in args
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10579] Use 
``int``
 type name consistently
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10448] Move 
``SyntaxShape``
 specifier parsing into own file
joergsch fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10577] line folding in 
``from ics``
/
``from vcf``
ClipplerBlood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10572] added a 
``--env``
 flag to the 
``do``
 command
rgwood did some work to simplify 
``explore``
: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10570] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10562] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10559] 3
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10569] made "can't follow stream paths" error a bit better
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10551] improved assertion error messages in 
``std assert``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10519] added 
``to ndjson``
 and 
``to nuon``
 to the standard library
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10566] added 
``--env``
 and 
``--wrapped``
 flags to 
``def``
brunerm99 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10565] added a warning to 
``url join``
 when input key is not supported (#10506)
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10564] update build flags for riscv64gc and armv7 targets
Yethal 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10545] reduced test file parsing overhead in the stdlib
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10526] changed the SyntaxShape of 
``-c``
 flag from list to record
vedaRadev 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10522] added a 'help escapes' command for quick reference of nushell string escapes
stormasm tweaked 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10587] eval.rs to remove pub from fn eval_element_with_input
